OL,3,C400 Scottish soldiers complete
OL,4,Cintensive training in Galloway Forest
OL,6,FFour hundred Scottish soldiers manning
OL,7,F40 patrol vehicles have completed
OL,8,Ftheir intensive training exercise in
OL,9,FGalloway Forest.
OL,11,FThe Royal Regiment of Scotland, the
OL,12,FScottish division of the British Army,
OL,13,Fspent up to three days in the forest,
OL,14,Fnear Newton Stewart, as part of a
OL,15,Flarger two-week operation known as
OL,16,F'Hector's Storm'. The two-week course
OL,17,Fhas also involved camps in England and
OL,18,FWales.
