OL,3,C400 Scottish soldiers complete
OL,4,Cintensive training in Galloway Forest
OL,6,FLt Col Gordon Muir, Commanding
OL,7,FOfficer, believes it has been a useful
OL,8,Ftraining programme in Galloway Forest.
OL,9,FHe said: "So we've had just sort of
OL,10,Fthree days of proper training in some
OL,11,Fpretty demanding terrain, which has
OL,12,Fbeen really really useful for the team.
OL,14,F"And I think one that they've pretty
OL,15,Fmuch enjoyed - apart from a few
OL,16,Fincidents of getting up to their waist
OL,17,Fand deeper in bogs and everything else
OL,18,F- they've generally enjoyed it."
OL,20,FThe Scottish division brought vehicles
OL,21,Fsuch as the 7.5-ton Foxhound.
