OL,3,C400 Scottish soldiers complete
OL,4,Cintensive training in Galloway Forest
OL,6,FThe soldiers have been engaging in
OL,7,Frural combat and survival exercises,
OL,8,Fas well as having to sleep outdoors
OL,9,Fand live off rations.
OL,11,FGalloway Forest has been marked an
OL,12,Fideal training ground due to its dense
OL,13,Fwoodlands and challenging terrain,
OL,14,Fensuring they are well-prepared for
OL,15,Fdeployment in a variety of
OL,16,Fenvironments abroad.
